            "title": "萬科洽短期貸款 據悉兩銀行拒絕",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"萬科洽短期貸款 據悉兩銀行拒絕\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2V7leyCJS0WKvK6N3XmmbA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/668f0f10-cbeb-11f0-bbff-b8fb53fa60fd\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">萬科洽短期貸款 據悉兩銀行拒絕</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
